Second Department,

November, 1951.

(November 19, 1951.) In the Matter of Freda K. Ralph, Respondent, against Board of Estimate of the City of New York et al., Appellants.

Motion to dismiss appeal granted, without costs, and appeal dismissed, without costs. Present — Carswell, Acting P. J., Johnston, Adel, Wenzel and MacCrate, JJ.
